docs.text: Resources for teaching AI to Students Ages 8-18 Google Tensorflow Playground This site is excellent for helping you visualize how neural networks classify object. The interactive tool allows you to change the number of neurons and layers in a neural network and see how these changes impact a simple classifier. Google Tensorflow Playground
